Reset their password on any linked first-party platforms.

So please do me a favour.

source: Thank you for getting in touch about this, I can understand this must be concerning for you, I will certainly try my best to help you.

source: To begin with, may I know the email originally linked with your PRS-ORG Account?

source: I have shared a 6 digit code to your email, please share it with me.

source: Check your security and activate Login Verification on your email account.

Reset your password on any linked First-Party platforms.

Your PRS-ORG Account has been secured now.

source: 해킹을 당해서 사라진 영웅파편과 금속재료를 복구해주실 수 있을까요?

source: Unfortunately, we do not support PRS-ORG missing content in case of hacked account, since the items stay in the game only.
reference: 안타깝게도 해킹된 계정의 경우 PRS-ORG에서 누락된 콘텐츠를 지원하고 있지는 않습니다.이는 아이템이 게임에만 남아 있기 때문입니다.

source: 해커가 제 아이디를 썼다는 로그인 기록도 가지고 있고요.
reference: I also have login records that show the hacker used my username.

source: I totally understand your concern, but unfortunately we can not restore those items as we do not have the option to so.

source: Since nothing can be stolen from it as it does not have platform to transfer things from one account to another.

source: 영웅파편을 얻기 위해 소비하는 돈이 절대 적지 않고 그걸 NAME-M님도 알고 계시잖아요.
reference: The amount of money spent to get hero shards is never small, and you know it, NAME-M.

source: I totally understand your concern, but unfortunately it is not possible to restore it, I can only help you with securing the PRS-ORG Account.

I'm not saying it was stolen.

reference: 파편이나 재료를 사용했더라도 고객님의 계정에서만 사용되었을 것입니다. PRS-ORG에서 어떤 것도 훔칠 수 없음을 이해해 주시기 바랍니다.

source: Is there anything else I can assist you with?

reference: I'm not saying that they got stollen.

source: 전 그 시간에 일을 하고 있었어요.

source: Apart from this, is there anything else I can assist you with?

Can you tell us your name?

source: 해킹의심사례에 대한 해결결과에 대한 얘기를 듣지 못해 채팅을 요청했습니다.
reference: I hadn't heard anything about the resolution of the suspected hacking case, so I requested a chat.

source: Hi NAME-M, it's nice to meet you and I hope you are doing well.

I hope you can expedite this.

source: Looks like your account has been already secured by the previous advisor and the chat was disconnected while investigating about the missing content.
reference: 고객님의 계정은 이미 이전 상담원에 의해 보호되었으며 누락된 콘텐츠에 대해 조사하는 동안 채팅이 끊어진 것 같습니다.

source: In order to verify your account, I have sent a verification code on your email, please check if you have received an email with the subject line "Please verify ownership of your PRS-ORG Account" in your inbox or spam inbox and share it with me.

source: Have you checked if your PRS-ORG has still the same name?

source: 클럽명은 동일하나 선수와 거래가능카드와 코인, 모으고 있던 카드팩이 모두 사라졌네요.
reference: The name of the club is the same, but everything is gone such as the players, tradable cards, coins, and card packs I've been collecting.

source: Kindly share the missing content details.
reference: 누락된 콘텐츠 세부 정보를 공유해 주세요.

source: 팩은 10개정도 모았던거 같고, 코인은 28만코인정도, 거래가능카드는 30명쯤 될거 같음
reference: I think I've collected about 10 packs, 280,000 coins, and about 30 tradable cards.

source: May I know the name of the players that you are missing?
reference: 누락된 선수의 이름을 알 수 있을까요?

source: I don't want to rush you here but since we have been idle for few minutes, I want to make sure if we are still connected, are we?
reference: 서두르고 싶지는 않지만 고객님께서는 몇 분 동안 유휴 상태였기 때문에 아직 연결되어 있는지 확인하고 싶습니다.
NAME-N, that's all I can think of.

source: 주전으로 등록했던 선수를 따로 사진으로 남겼던게 아니구요.
reference: I didn't take a picture of the player who was listed as a starter.

source: Have you lost any untradeable player as well?
거래불가한 선수는 급매로 날렸는데 얼마나 되는지는 잘 모르겠네요.
reference: Untradeable players were sold off, but I'm not sure how many.
I'm pretty sure at least a couple of 87+ were deleted.
아래 면책 조항를 읽어 주시기 바랍니다.

source: When we review an account for loss, compromise, or missing items, we review all past activity on the account.
reference: 분실, 손상 또는 누락된 아이템에 대해 계정을 검토할 때 계정의 모든 과거 활동을 검토합니다.

source: Players that falsely claim a lost item or have been sending and receiving Coins are breaking our rules in the User Agreement.
reference: 분실물을 허위로 청구하거나 코인을 주고받은 플레이어는 사용자 계약의 규칙을 위반하는 것입니다.

source: When our User Agreement is broken, we often have to suspend gameplay or close accounts.
reference: 사용자 계약이 파기되면 종종 게임플레이를 일시 중단하거나 계정을 폐쇄해야 합니다.

source: This helps us ensure a fun, secure, and fair environment for all players.
reference: 이를 통해 모든 플레이어에게 재미있고 안전하며 공정한 환경을 제공할 수 있습니다.

source: Do you still agree to move forward with your account review?
reference: 여전히 계정 검토를 진행하는 데 동의하십니까?

source: Let me inform you that we'll review your case, and reach out to you  once we have more updates; in the meantime, you  can check your case status via PRS-ORG Help.
reference: 케이스를 검토하고 추가 업데이트 사항이 있으면 다시 연락드리도록 하겠습니다. 그동안 PRS-ORG 고객 지원을 통해 케이스 상태를 확인하실 수 있습니다.
We hope to hear from you next time.

source: You have been amazingly calm and cooperative, much appreciated.
reference: 고객님께서는 놀라울 정도로 침착하고 협조적이었습니다. 대단히 감사했습니다.

source: Anything else from me at this moment!

source: If you allow me I will dispute the ban to our terms of Services team.

source: they will investigate and if possible will try to overturn the ban.

source: the result totally depends on their investigation but from my end, I will share all the detail you have shared with me in my note.

source: Don't worry, To help you further one steps head with your issue and to get the issue resolved for you as soon as possible, I will personally ask our TOS team to look into the case and to get it resolved soon.
reference: 걱정하지 마세요. 문제를 최대한 빨리 해결할 수 있도록 TOS 팀에서 해당 케이스를 조사하여 빠른 시일 내에 해결될 수 있도록 직접 요청하겠습니다.
